release_note: What s New in Theia: Enhancing Your Journey to Personal Growth We are excited to bring you the latest update of Theia packed with improvements and fixes to ensure your journey towards personal growth and wellness is smoother than ever. Here s what we ve been working on: Notification Bug Fixed: We ve squashed that pesky notification bug that was causing issues for some users. Now you ll receive all your important reminders and insights without a hitch. AI Model Enhancement: The heart of Theia our advanced AI model has received a substantial update. It s now even smarter more intuitive and better equipped to tailor its responses and guidance to your unique journey. Screen Size and Flickering Issues Resolved: We ve ironed out the wrinkles with screen size adaptability on various devices ensuring a seamless and visually pleasing experience across the board. Additionally we ve eliminated the screen flickering issue that some of our users reported. Habits Tracking Now More Reliable: Your habit tracking is crucial to your journey of personal growth. We ve addressed and fixed the bug that was causing habits not to save properly. Now you can trust Theia to accurately track and reflect on your progress. Backend Server Optimization: In our continuous effort to provide a fast and reliable experience we ve optimized our backend servers especially when it comes to handling changes in models. This means quicker response times and a smoother interaction with Theia. Your Feedback Matters: We are listening and your feedback is invaluable to us. We are committed to making Theia the best it can be and we rely on your insights and suggestions to guide our improvements. Please keep the feedback coming! Help Us Shape Theia: Send Your Feedback! Your experience and insights are what drive us to do better. If you have thoughts on how we can improve features you d like to see or any issues you want us to address please reach out through our in app feedback form or contact us at support theia app.com. Together we can ensure that Theia continues to be the AI driven force for personal growth and well being that you deserve. Thank you for being a valued part of the Theia community!

What s New in This Update: Major Enhancements: Adaptive Learning: Theia now learns faster and more intuitively from your interactions crafting a more personalized journey for you. Enhanced Meditation Revamped UI: A sleeker more user friendly interface for smoother navigation and a richer experience. Security Upgrades: We ve fortified our data protection measures ensuring your journey remains private and secure.
